{"tid":1095354,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人食過河豚？有毒,但日本好受歡迎 !","createTime":"2019-04-07T03:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T15:22:41.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b87c1f06d32119b1a8503a623f93ae1c169788d4","tid":1095354,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:30:05.000Z","msg":"河豚的皮和內臟是有毒，所以宰殺過程要小心，中毒者沒有解藥。這種海鮮在日本很受歡迎，但宰殺過程都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/awq8MotdCyk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fawq8MotdCyk&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=03206448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/awq8MotdCyk</a>"},{"pid":"081b5fe47ca1a78a95623067b3c53489b8b96ec7","tid":1095354,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"有沒有人吃過？好不好吃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2fe4bf9df9cfe681d3f248759dbb9deeaede10","tid":1095354,"uid":33359,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T04:04:14.000Z","msg":"好食但很貴"},{"pid":"2bc3cf584a14182b9d13c00837a3ebed0a218ec7","tid":1095354,"uid":34197,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T04:09:01.000Z","msg":"上個月去大阪食咗兩轉,5500yen一餐,一次食燒河豚,另一次就打邊爐,抵唔抵食見人見志,但係我就覺得係自己地頭食唔到嘅嘢就係抵食"},{"pid":"4bda3a8b79d6a4b9cf1c925fb28aede3aa745096","tid":1095354,"uid":58413,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"其實點解仲未解到毒？"},{"pid":"220955a1df8d188f18b857e1be826b9598518ad7","tid":1095354,"uid":6222,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"食過2次<br />\n<br />\n好食<br />\n<br />\n首先食皮 已經切成絲 食落好爽好彈<br />\n<br />\n之後上刺身 配蘿蔔蓉同柚子醋 食落有咬口同鮮<br />\n<br />\n再黎上炸嘅 食落似雞肉/田雞 但仲嫩口過雞肉/田雞 <br />\n<br />\n然後加水落鍋食烚嘅 <br />\n<br />\n最後就係鍋加蛋 紫菜 飯煮成粥"},{"pid":"b36715bb5f489a606f30c4686eb1728a7b33499b","tid":1095354,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"下次我去日本時又試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過上面video 來看，宰殺過程都幾慘，脫皮後仲掙扎緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcbc753d4c1d5be2bdfa825243bc90dcf77da40","tid":1095354,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"我細細個阿婆就煲雞泡干湯比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd45bbf8ac5f87a2f18bc356bf22a19d44adc28c","tid":1095354,"uid":80724,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"一值好想試，但唔知邊間安全同好食，有無推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw，高級河豚料理聽講可以貴到幾千港紙一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72dc9085c4deaaeb52a9e64a2a32e1a0eaa59fe","tid":1095354,"uid":109104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"我就覺得硬咗少少 味道ok 唔錯"},{"pid":"50820b2cb5a9c3d5b70510ed5521fc85d77e1317","tid":1095354,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bcbc753d4c1d5be2bdfa825243bc90dcf77da40","tid":1095354,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"我細細個阿婆就煲雞泡干湯比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:50:21.000Z","msg":"一個唔覺意就玩完"},{"pid":"ed5666007421a4085a7020a43574ff7b4d0b77db","tid":1095354,"uid":221490,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50820b2cb5a9c3d5b70510ed5521fc85d77e1317","tid":1095354,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bcbc753d4c1d5be2bdfa825243bc90dcf77da40","tid":1095354,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"我細細個阿婆就煲雞泡干湯比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:50:21.000Z","msg":"一個唔覺意就玩完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:52:50.000Z","msg":"我阿婆水上人 我媽咪都係食雞泡干食大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c5560f98779897e6c802569f2215f92dfc193e","tid":1095354,"uid":52765,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:55:03.000Z","msg":"日本食過虎豚/韓國食三湖，日本真係一般，韓國好食好多"},{"pid":"b7bba5bc52a6ef21afc2cc4d0cdbe262e9f4bc24","tid":1095354,"uid":33875,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:58:40.000Z","msg":"係名古屋食過一次，三個人埋單一萬Yen內，本身食咗野再去所以叫一份餐，另外兩個人唔叫餐要收返搭枱錢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gJmACoX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gJmACoX</a><br />\n<br />\n爽滑口感唔似一般魚刺身，似軟身貝類海產。最好食係「白子」，香滑濃郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3adf7e04e2d832798a79403e808b445e2a051dd","tid":1095354,"uid":172042,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd45bbf8ac5f87a2f18bc356bf22a19d44adc28c","tid":1095354,"uid":80724,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"一值好想試，但唔知邊間安全同好食，有無推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw，高級河豚料理聽講可以貴到幾千港紙一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"天然河豚唔計酒水通常都係三萬円左右一餐啫，唔係好貴，不過通常秋冬先有"},{"pid":"2672c06d1f494ce67d31aeefc5800e98d60aa0ea","tid":1095354,"uid":244137,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"一般劏魚都會整暈/插落個腦到先，務求減少條魚既痛苦<br />\n同埋唔好令條魚受驚，過度消耗三磷酸腺苷變做乳酸，最後搞到魚身變僵<br />\n日本師傅劏都會插落河豚個腦到先，呢個moment既河豚都已經腦死，後面喐動都係神經反應<br />\n但係你條link冇殺左條河豚先，似虐待河豚多d，整出來都冇殺左先咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a932ace684c5fbaef2d985b86545a8fd7f141c","tid":1095354,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0166e3e8951f833d2a819f2389c05e94db31e43","tid":1095354,"uid":57674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"之前食鐵板牛個陣食過<br />\n食之前個師傅仲見我地好疑惑<br />\n話俾我地聽係河豚黎 但人工飼養 唔使擔心毒素問題<br />\n不過唔大舊 都OK好味<br />\nBTW 個師傅真係識廣東話 成程食得勁開心"},{"pid":"2501505ba74349fb37877da1bcc520ca54a78e31","tid":1095354,"uid":100016,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"樓主收皮啦屌你老母, 食兔肉就唔撚得, 食河豚就好好味??"},{"pid":"d972d0720b4982c9a8af44cc32e39984ac1c7d2e","tid":1095354,"uid":7840,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67fb0668a96f3a139598a5ca73cb65d76a546a0d","tid":1095354,"uid":244137,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d972d0720b4982c9a8af44cc32e39984ac1c7d2e","tid":1095354,"uid":7840,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2672c06d1f494ce67d31aeefc5800e98d60aa0ea","tid":1095354,"uid":244137,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"一般劏魚都會整暈/插落個腦到先，務求減少條魚既痛苦<br />\n同埋唔好令條魚受驚，過度消耗三磷酸腺苷變做乳酸，最後搞到魚身變僵<br />\n日本師傅劏都會插落河豚個腦到先，呢個moment既河豚都已經腦死，後面喐動都係神經反應<br />\n但係你條link冇殺左條河豚先，似虐待河豚多d，整出來都冇殺左先咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"魚係有完整既神經系統，點會唔會痛<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/food/wp/2018/05/24/scientists-say-fish-feel-pain-it-could-lead-to-major-changes-in-the-fishing-industry/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Ffood%2Fwp%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2Fscientists-say-fish-feel-pain-it-could-lead-to-major-changes-in-the-fishing-industry%2F&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=8c21b4d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/food/wp/2018/05/24/scientists-say-fish-feel-pain-it-could-lead-to-major-changes-in-the-fishing-industry/</a>"},{"pid":"43b53f261c8dccb50ac1d84fabd598274d25ec6d","tid":1095354,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42904431d1a3f0b3e6aeb40d12e71a82edf7269f","tid":1095354,"uid":40632,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"日本識一個老主廚 有次請我一條友食成條既份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但d刺身同皮其實冇乜味 得個口感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但聽講大陸江蘇都有個地方係食河豚 個邊D人係話唔食肝不如唔好食 但肝係最毒個位 好撚危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8d57f1e5fd526bfbab32dc1250b04e551cf46d","tid":1095354,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed5666007421a4085a7020a43574ff7b4d0b77db","tid":1095354,"uid":221490,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50820b2cb5a9c3d5b70510ed5521fc85d77e1317","tid":1095354,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bcbc753d4c1d5be2bdfa825243bc90dcf77da40","tid":1095354,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"我細細個阿婆就煲雞泡干湯比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:50:21.000Z","msg":"一個唔覺意就玩完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:52:50.000Z","msg":"我阿婆水上人 我媽咪都係食雞泡干食大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"好似唔同品種其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f902fc6a78d4859b04612a8b3399e7762e0967c","tid":1095354,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"而家有養殖河豚，冇毒"},{"pid":"abb7edc3c27be5ee83481a14c35bbea6c9895dcf","tid":1095354